data.oai_dc:dc: The "Type Specimens" database contains information on: Anoplura, Coleoptera (Curculionidae, Bruchinae, Scolytidae, Platypodidae, Erotylidae), Collembola, Diptera (Agromyzidae, Borboridae), Hemiptera (Membracidae, Fulgoridae, Achilidae, Cixiidae, Tropiduchidae), Hymenoptera (Evanioidea, Stephanoidea, Braconidae (pars), Ichneumonidae (described by G. Enderlein), Lepidoptera (pars), Mallophaga, Plecoptera. Material is preserved in the Zoological Collection MIZ. The database will be updated.|2,340 occurrences
